    rdfs:comment 'The exact contractually mandated credit language or text that must appear on screen or in promotional materials (e.g., \'Directed by\', \'Written by\', \'Starring\', \'A Film By\', \'Executive Producer\'). | Column credit_text (STRING) in talent.credit_attribution' ;
