    rdfs:comment 'The geographic territory or market where the advertiser has rights to use the talent\'s likeness and endorsement (e.g., \'North America\', \'Global\', \'EU + UK\'). This is deal-specific and varies by advertiser. | Column usage_territory (STRING) in talent.endorsement_deal' ;
